text: Antal Steer (born 10 October 1943) is a Hungarian wrestler. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Hungary Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Wrestlers at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bratislava
